%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20Want%20To%20Tease%20People%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Vs%20Opposition%20On%20Non-Veg%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20over%20a%20video%20of%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20eating%20fish%20snowballed%20on%20Friday%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20RJD%20leader%2C%20his%20father%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20are%20exhibiting%20thoughts%20from%20the%20Mughal%20era.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20opposition%20of%20indulging%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20appeasement%20and%20going%20after%20a%20particular%20vote%20bank%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20claimed%20that%20such%20videos%20are%20being%20posted%20during%20periods%20considered%20auspicious%20by%20Hindus%20to%20tease%20and%20annoy%20most%20of%20India's%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftejashwi-yadavs-counter-after-video-of-him-eating-fish-sparks-row-5411311%5C%22%3Ehad%20clarified%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20video%20was%20shot%20a%20day%20before%20Navratri%20began%20and%20was%20uploaded%20to%20%26quot%3Btest%20the%20IQ%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Godi%20media%20followers%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20BJP's%20politics%20is%20limited%20to%20what%20people%20are%20eating%20and%20wearing%20because%20its%20governments%20have%20not%20done%20anything%20for%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20at%20Udhampur%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20a%20week%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20PM%20Modi%20referred%20to%20a%20video%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Lalu%20Yadav%20cooking%20mutton%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20are%20not%20bothered%20about%20the%20feelings%20of%20most%20of%20the%20country's%20population.%20During%20Sawan%20(an%20auspicious%20month%20in%20the%20Hindu%20calendar)%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20the%20house%20of%20a%20convicted%20man%20and%20cooking%20mutton.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20they%20are%20also%20putting%20up%20videos%20and%20teasing%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20does%20not%20stop%20anyone%20from%20eating%20anything%2C%20and%20neither%20does%20Modi%2C%20but%20their%20intention%20is%20different.%20When%20the%20Mughals%20attacked%2C%20they%20were%20not%20satisfied%20with%20defeating%20the%20king%20alone.%20They%20did%20not%20get%20satisfaction%20until%20they%20destroyed%20temples...%20they%20enjoyed%20doing%20this.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20by%20uploading%20the%20video%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Sawan%2C%20they%20(the%20opposition)%20are%20exhibiting%20the%20thoughts%20of%20the%20Mughal%20era%2C%20attempting%20to%20tease%20people%20and%20fortify%20their%20vote%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraining%20his%20guns%20on%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20without%20naming%20him%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20uploading%20a%20video%20of%20consuming%20non-vegetarian%20food%20during%20Navratra%20was%20also%20an%20attempt%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20are%20you%20trying%20to%20please%20by%20hurting%20the%20sentiments%20of%20people%3F%20I%20know%20these%20people%20will%20now%20shower%20abuses%20on%20me%20for%20saying%20this%2C%20but%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20in%20a%20democracy%20to%20tell%20people%20what%20is%20right%20when%20lines%20are%20crossed%2C%20and%20I%20am%20doing%20my%20duty.%20They%20do%20this%20deliberately%20to%20attack%20the%20country's%20beliefs%2C%20so%20that%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20country%20watches%20their%20videos%20and%20gets%20uncomfortable.%20They%20have%20gone%20beyond%20appeasement%20and%20are%20giving%20evidence%20of%20their%20Mughal-like%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20his%20charge%20of%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20the%20PM%20said%20the%20opposition%20does%20not%20know%20that%20when%20the%20people%20decide%2C%20princes%20(%3Cem%3E'yuvraj'%3C%2Fem%3E)%20from%20big%20royal%20families%20have%20to%20give%20up%20their%20thrones.%20The%20%3Cem%3E'yuvraj'%3C%2Fem%3E%20jibe%20has%20been%20used%20by%20the%20PM%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20past%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20Talking%20About%20Issues'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20rally%20on%20Friday%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20reacted%20to%20the%20PM's%20remarks%20without%20naming%20him%20and%20said%20that%2C%20instead%20of%20talking%20about%20the%20issues%20that%20matter%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20focusing%20on%20what%20people%20are%20eating%20and%20wearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20not%20talking%20about%20the%20issues%20of%20Bihar%2C%20how%20they%20will%20stop%20migration%20from%20the%20state%20or%20what%20they%20will%20do%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20if%20they%20are%20voted%20to%20power.%20And%20what%20will%20they%20say%3F%20They%20have%20done%20nothing%20in%2010%20years%20(at%20the%20Centre)%20and%2017%20years%20(in%20Bihar)...%20They%20will%20keep%20talking%20about%20what%20people%20are%20wearing%20and%20eating%2C%20and%20centre%20their%20politics%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712924640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcqoh4cdg_pm-modi-udhampur_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-they-want-to-tease-people-pm-vs-opposition-on-non-veg-food-5426478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20over%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20allegedly%20consuming%20fish%20during%20Navratri%20snowballed%20on%20Friday%20with%20the%20PM%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20opposition%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20are%20exhibiting%20thoughts%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Mughal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engag