in%20a%20partnership%20firm%20established%20by%20the%20trio%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20Pandya%20brothers%2C%20along%20with%20Vaibhav%2C%20ventured%20into%20the%20polymer%20business%2C%20with%20each%20sibling%20having%20a%20defined%20stake%20in%20the%20enterprise.%20Hardik%20and%20Krunal%20were%20to%20contribute%2040%20per%20cent%20each%20to%20the%20capital%2C%20while%20Vaibhav's%20share%20stood%20at%2020%20per%20cent.%20The%20arrangement%20stipulated%20that%20profits%20would%20be%20distributed%20among%20the%20partners%20in%20proportion%20to%20their%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20has%20come%20to%20light%20that%20Vaibhav%20allegedly%20diverted%20profits%20from%20the%20partnership%20firm%20into%20his%20personal%20accounts%2C%20thereby%20diminishing%20the%20returns%20due%20to%20Hardik%20and%20Krunal.%20He%20also%20increased%20his%20profit%20share%20to%2033.3%20per%20cent%20secretly%2C%20resulting%20in%20substantial%20losses%20for%20the%20other%20Pandya%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20escalated%20when%20Vaibhav%20allegedly%20transferred%20funds%20from%20the%20partnership%20account%20to%20another%20company%20without%20the%20knowledge%20or%20consent%20of%20his%20brothers%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20financial%20strain%20on%20Hardik%20and%20Krunal's%20business%20interests.%20They%20suffered%20a%20loss%20of%20nearly%20Rs%204.3%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20discovering%20these%20discrepancies%2C%20Hardik%20and%20Krunal%20confronted%20Vaibhav%2C%20only%20to%20be%20met%20with%20threats%20of%20defamation%20should%20they%20pursue%20legal%20action%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Pandya%20brothers'%20accountant%20lodged%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20at%20Khar%20police%20station%2C%20prompting%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20authorities.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20for%20further%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20thorough%20investigation%2C%20Vaibhav%20Pandya%20was%20placed%20under%20arrest%20and%20remanded%20to%20police%20custody%20for%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya%20has%20been%20making%20the%20headlines%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year's%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20on%20April%2022.%20He%20replaced%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20has%20led%20MI%20to%205%20championship%20titles%2C%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20IPL%20side.%20The%20management's%20decision%20to%20change%20the%20captains%20hasn't%20gone%20down%20with%20some%20fans%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20has%20been%20booed%20during%20all%20of%20MI's%20matches%2C%20including%20those%20at%20their%20homeground%20Wankhede.%20It%20hasn't%20helped%20his%20cause%20that%20Mumbai%20lost%20their%20first%203%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712922180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fd9fi4lek_hardik-pandya-afp_625x300_12_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-hardik-pandya-rs-4-crore-fraud-case-against-stepbrother-that-landed-him-in-jail-5426794%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vaibhav%20Pandya%2C%20the%20stepbrother%20of%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captain%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Police's%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20on%20charges%20of%20fraud%20amounting%20to%20Rs%204.3%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-hardik-pandya-rs-4-crore-fraud-case-against-stepbrother-that-landed-him-in-jail-5426794%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-hardik-pandya-rs-4-crore-fraud-case-against-stepbrother-that-landed-him-in-jail-5426794%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-hardik-pandya-rs-4-crore-fraud-case-agai