t%20how%20he%20had%20to%20rush%20his%20bleeding%20mother%20and%20sister%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20they%20were%20shot.%20He%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20carry%20my%20mother%20and%20my%20sister%20to%20the%20hospital%20while%20they%20were%20bleeding.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAur%20us%20waqt%20mujhe%20pta%20nahi%20tha%20ki%20mujhe%20bhi%20goli%20lagi%20thi%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%5BAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20that%20I%20was%20also%20shot%5D%20actually.%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETo%20doctor%20ne%20bola%20ki%2C%20%E2%80%98tumhari%20shirt%20par%20itna%20khun%20kyu%20hai%3F'%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%5BThe%20doctor%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20is%20there%20so%20much%20blood%20on%20your%20shirt%3F'%5D%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20it%20must%20be%20from%20my%20mother%20or%20sister.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20you%20have%20been%20shot.%20We%20don't%20have%20enough%20place%20over%20here.%20You%20have%20to%20go%20to%20another%20hospital.'%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20you%20just%20keep%20my%20mother%20and%20sister%20alive.%20And%20I%20also%20was%20trying%20to%20check%20on%20my%20father%20what%20he%20was%20going%20to%20be%20doing%20at%20that%20point.%E2%80%9D%20Then%2C%20the%20actor%20explained%20how%20his%20friend%20named%20Abis%20took%20him%20to%20another%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETalking%20about%20how%20it%20all%20happened%20on%20the%20day%20of%20his%20birthday%20(October%2021)%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fit-will-always-be-a-turning-point-in-my-career-kajol-on-29-years-of-udhaar-ki-zindagi-4545475%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1712999166983000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0v5DLilxNrbMXqiVQOh2eB%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fit-will-always-be-a-turning-point-in-my-career-kajol-on-29-years-of-udhaar-ki-zindagi-4545475%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamal%20Sadanah%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had