es.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fanti-ageing-activist-sparks-controversy-with-picture-of-his-face%2Famp_articleshow%2F109243193.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTime%20Not%20Far%20When%20Assembly%20Elections%20Will%20Be%20Held%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20the%20time%20is%20not%20far%20when%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20will%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20share%20their%20issues%20with%20ministers%20and%20legislators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20development%20projects%20undertaken%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20are%20just%20a%20%26quot%3Btrailer%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20to%20work%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20fabulous%20picture%20of%20a%20new%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20completely%20changed%20and%20the%20biggest%20thing%20is%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20as%20people%20have%20moved%20from%20disappointments%20towards%20hope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20is%20not%20far%20when%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20will%20also%20get%20its%20statehood%20back.%20You%20will%20again%20raise%20your%20issues%20with%20your%20legislators%20and%20ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20told%20a%20rally%20organised%20to%20garner%20support%20for%20Union%20minister%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20from%20Udhampur%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20asserted%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20issues%20of%20every%20section%20of%20the%20society%26quot%3B%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20his%20vision%20of%20carving%20out%20a%20vibrant%20picture%20of%20a%20new%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20said%20people%20are%20saying%20a%20lot%20has%20been%20done%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20the%20worst%2C%20so%20this%20looks%20like%20a%20lot%20to%20you.%20You%20feel%20good%20to%20see%20development.%20But%20Modi%20thinks%20bigger.%20Modi%20has%20a%20great%20vision.%20Whatever%20has%20happened%20till%20now%20is%20just%20a%20trailer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20ongoing%20road%20and%20tunnel%20construction%20projects%20will%20be%20completed%20at%20a%20fast%20pace.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20and%20factories%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20outside%20will%20come%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20New%20railway%2C%20tunnel%20and%20road%20projects%20are%20coming%20up.%20A%20record%20number%20of%20tourists%20are%20coming%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20to%20become%20a%20start-up%20hub%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20new%20phase%20is%20becoming%20the%20destiny%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20dream%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20several%20generations.%20I%20give%20you%20the%20guarantee%20that%20your%20dream%20is%20my%20resolution.%20Every%20moment%20of%20fulfilling%20your%20dream%20is%20dedicated%20to%20you.%20These%20efforts%20will%20be%20in%20the%20name%20of%20India.%20It%20will%20change%20the%20destiny%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20government%20will%20work%20round%20the%20clock%20to%20realise%20the%20dream%20of%20%26quot%3BViksit%20Bharat%202047%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20guarantee%20of%20Modi.%20In%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20we%20have%20cracked%20down%20on%20terrorism%20and%20corruption%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20we