ges%2Famp_articleshow%2F109243679.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Impact%20Will%20New%20UK%20Family%20Visa%20Rule%20Have%20On%20Indians%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Kingdom%20has%20implemented%20new%20visa%20and%20income%20regulations%20as%20part%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20plans%20to%20cut%20down%20immigration%20levels.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20changes%20the%20minimum%20income%20required%20to%20sponsor%20family%20members%20has%20been%20raised%20significantly%2C%20creating%20a%20concern%20for%20Indian%20migrants.%20Those%20who%20earn%20less%20than%2029%2C000%20pounds%2C%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20sponsor%20a%20family%20member's%20visa%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20is%20a%20significant%2055%25%20rise%20from%20the%20current%20income%20benchmark%20-%2018%2C600%20pounds.%20And%20the%20benchmark%20will%20rise%20to%2038%2C700%20pounds%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20earnings%20of%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20people%20who%20migrated%20to%20the%20UK%20from%20India%20was%20less%20than%2039%2C000%20pounds%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20migration%20observatory%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Indians%20represent%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20non-EU%20immigration%20into%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20substantial%20numbers%20arriving%20for%20study-related%20purposes.%20The%20surge%20in%20visas%20granted%20to%20dependents%20from%20India%20and%20Nigeria%20underscores%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20family%20migration%20within%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndians%20have%20also%20consistently%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%20beneficiaries%20of%20skilled%20work%20visas%2C%20with%20a%20notable%20increase%20observed%20in%20the%20'Skilled%20Worker%20-%20Health%20and%20Care'%20category.%20The%20number%20of%20such%20visas%20issued%20to%20Indians%20saw%20a%2063%20per%20cent%20hike%20from%2013%2C380%20in%202021-22%20to%2021%2C837%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUK%20Home%20Office%20data%20show%20that%20Indian%20nationals%20represented%2038%25%20of%20all%20dependants%20issued%20a%20work%20visa%20alongside%20main%20applicants%2C%20followed%20by%20Nigerian%20and%20Zimbabwean%20nationals%20(17%25%20and%209%25%2C%20respectively).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20changes%20in%20the%20family%20visa%20rules%20will%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20many%20Indian%20workers%20to%20meet%20the%20new%20criteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20to%20increase%20the%20income%20threshold%20to%20sponsor%20a%20family%20member's%20visa%2C%20initiated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20and%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%2C%20aims%20to%20curb%20legal%20migration%20and%20alleviate%20taxpayer%20burdens%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UK%20Home%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECleverly%20emphasized%20the%20necessity%20of%20reducing%20migration%20levels%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20complexities%20and%20challenges%20inherent%20in%20achieving%20a%20balance%20acceptable%20to%20the%20British%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712913960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjdvn8lg4_london_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplained-what-impact-will-new-uk-family-visa-rule-have-on-indians-5425867%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20Kingdom%20has%20implemented%20new%20visa%20and%20income%20regulations%20as%20part%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20plans%20to%20cut%20down%20immigration%20levels.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20changes%20the%20minimum%20income%20required%20to%20sponsor%20family%20members%20has%20been%20raised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fexplained-what-impact-will-new-uk-family-visa-rule-have-on-indians-5425867%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww