Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-william-makes-first-appearance-since-wifes-cancer-announcement%2Famp_articleshow%2F109242923.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprince-william-makes-first-appearance-since-wifes-cancer-announcement%2Famp_articleshow%2F109242923.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Excessive%20Screen%20Time%20Causing%20Dry%20Eyes%3F%20Here's%20How%20To%20Manage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDry%20eyes%20can%20be%20a%20persistent%20problem%20for%20many%20individuals%2C%20causing%20discomfort%20and%20sometimes%20even%20affecting%20daily%20activities.%20Its%20syndrome%20occurs%20when%20the%20eyes%20do%20not%20produce%20enough%20tears%20or%20evaporate%20too%20quickly%2C%20and%20the%20eyes%20aren't%20lubricated%20adequately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20can%20result%20in%20irritation%2C%20redness%2C%20sensitivity%20to%20light%2C%20and%20a%20gritty%20sensation%20in%20the%20eyes.%20Whether%20due%20to%20environmental%20factors%2C%20prolonged%20screen%20time%2C%20or%20underlying%20health%20conditions%2C%20managing%20dry%20eyes%20effectively%20is%20crucial%20for%20maintaining%20eye%20health%20and%20overall%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETips%20For%20Relief%20And%20Comfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20Hydrated%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EProper%20hydration%20is%20essential%20for%20overall%20health%2C%20including%20eye%20health.%20Drinking%20an%20adequate%20amount%20of%20water%20throughout%20the%20day%20can%20help%20maintain%20tear%20production%20and%20prevent%20dryness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20Artificial%20Tear%20Drops%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver-the-counter%20artificial%20tear%20drops%20can%20provide%20immediate%20relief%20by%20lubricating%20the%20eyes%20and%20alleviating%20dryness.%20It's%20important%20to%20choose%20preservative-free%20drops%20and%20use%20them%20as%20needed%2C%20following%20the%20instructions%20on%20the%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlink%20Regularly%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESpending%20long%20periods%20staring%20at%20screens%20can%20lead%20to%20decreased%20blinking%2C%20which%20can%20exacerbate%20dry%20eyes.%20Therefore%2C%20make%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20blink%20regularly%2C%20especially%20when%20using%20computers%2C%20smartphones%2C%20or%20other%20digital%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20Breaks%20from%20Screens%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20reduce%20eye%20strain%20and%20dryness%20associated%20with%20prolonged%20screen%20time%2C%20follow%20the%2020-20-20%20rule%3A%20every%2020%20minutes%2C%20take%20a%2020-second%20break%2C%20and%20look%20at%20something%2020%20feet%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20a%20Humidifier%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDry%20indoor%20air%20can%20contribute%20to%20dry%20eyes.%20Using%20a%20humidifier%20at%20home%20can%20add%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20helping%20to%20prevent%20the%20evaporation%20of%20tears%20and%20maintain%20comfortable%20eye%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtect%20Your%20Eyes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWear%20wraparound%20sunglasses%20or%20goggles%20when%20outdoors%20to%20shield%20the%20eyes%20from%20wind%2C%20dust%2C%20and%20other%20environmental%20irritants%20that%20can%20exacerbate%20dryness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintain%20a%20Healthy%20Diet%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConsuming%20foods%20rich%20in%20omega-3%20fatty%20acids%2C%20such%20as%20salmon%2C%20flaxseeds%2C%20and%20walnuts%2C%20may%20help%20reduce%20inflammation%20and%20improve%20tear%20quality.%20Additionally%2C%20incorporating%20foods%20high%20in%20vitamins%20A%2C%20C%2C%20and%20E%20can%20support%20overall%20eye%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsult%20an%20Eye%20Care%20Professional%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20dry%20eye%20symptoms%20persist%20or%20worsen%20despite%20self-care%20measures%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20seek%20guidance%20from%20an%20eye%20care%20professional.%20They%20can%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20eye%20exam%20to%20deter