22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335795%2Fisro-project-scientist-divakar-channappa-first-organic-date-farmer-in-karnataka-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20dates%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Pilani.%20Last%20season%2C%20Mukesh%20harvested%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20dates%20which%20earned%20him%20a%20huge%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20his%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20commando%20to%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20up%20date%20farming%2C%20Mukesh%20worked%20as%20a%20commando%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%2015%20years.%20He%20specialised%20in%20counter-hijack%20operations%20to%20safeguard%20people.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20took%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20the%20NSG%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20work%2C%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20visit%2020%20countries.%20On%20my%20way%20from%20the%20airports%20to%20hotels%2C%20I%20would%20spare%20some%20time%20to%20visit%20nearby%20farms%20and%20learn%20about%20their%20technologies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAgriculture%20is%20in%20my%20DNA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20my%20father%20and%20grandfathers%20grow%20crops.%20But%20like%20them%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20grow%20traditional%20crops%20like%20mustard%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20grams.%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%20new%20technologies.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20crops%20that%20required%20less%20water%20to%20grow%20in%20our%20dry%20region%20of%20Rajasthan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Kh