0the%20right%20solutions%20for%20the%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishwanath%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIncidental%20stories%20of%20people%20standing%20in%20a%20queue%20where%20a%20borewell%20has%20broken%20down%20in%20an%20RO%20plant%20or%20of%20some%20person%20using%20wet%20wipes%20to%20wash%20themselves%20are%20not%20helpful%20at%20all.%20Yes%2C%20genuine%20problems%20in%20the%20city%20need%20to%20be%20highlighted%2C%20but%20if%20you%20chase%20problems%20all%20day%20with%20100%20cameras%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20crazy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20kind%20of%20reporting%20is%20not%20helping%20anyone%20at%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20%E2%80%94%20a%20civil%20engineer%20and%20urban%20planner%20with%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20water%20and%20sanitation%20sector%20%E2%80%94%20has%20previously%20worked%20on%20the%20Karnataka%20Water%20Policy%20in%202019.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20Trustee%20of%20the%20Biome%20Environmental%20Trust%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20424px)%20100vw%2C%20424px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-1712314633.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22424%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solutions%20to%20Bengaluru's%20water%20scarcity%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-1712314633.png%20424w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-1712314633-200x300.png%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-1712314633-150x225.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22636%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ES%20Vishwanath%2C%20aka%20%E2%80%98Zenrainman%E2%80%99%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20would%20he%20define%20the%20current%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20state.%20If%20you%20build%20your%20piped%20water%20network%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20city%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20less%20pressure%20on%20your%20aquifers%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20need%20to%20draw%20groundwater.%20Your%20borewells%20will%20have%20water%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20need%20for%20tanker%20water%20supply.%20Since%20you%E2%80%99ve%20not%20given%20piped%20water%20supply%20%5Bto%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20city%5D%2C%20then%20the%20solution%20lies%20in%20groundwater%20extraction.%20This%20means%20that%20when%20groundwater%20collapses%2C%20there%20is%20no%20alternative%20source%20of%20water%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%20point%20further%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20%5Bwater%5D%20problem%20in%20about%20three-fourths%20of%20the%20city.%20We%20got%201%2C470%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20%5Bper%20day%5D%20coming%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20%5Briver%5D%2C%20and%20there%20are%20about%201.1%20million%20%5Bpiped%20water%5D%20connections%20covering%2010%20people%20per%20connection.%20For%2011%20million%20residents%20of%20the%20city%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20problem.%20For%203%20to%203.5%20million%20people%20living%20in%20the%20outskirts%20dependent%20on%20groundwater%2C%20there%20are%20%5Bwater%20scarcity%5D%20problems%20in%20pockets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20the%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20issued%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fwater%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-bwssb-announces-20-water-cut-to-bulk-consumers-identifies-areas-bearing-the-brunt-94973%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20detailed%20list%20%3C%2Fa%3Emarking%20out%20areas%20most%20severely%20impacted%20by%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20gathered%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20Groundwater%20Authority%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fbengaluru-east-taluk-worst-affected-in-depleting-groundwater-levels-this-summer%2Farticle68002688.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%2029%20March%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20of%20groundwater%20levels%20for%20last%20December%20and%20this%20January%20and%20February%20shows%20that%20Bengaluru%20East%20taluk%2C%20which%20houses%20one%20of%20the%20major%20IT%20corridors%20of%20the%20city%2C%20where%20the%20water%20crisis%20is%20most%20severe%20and%20groundwater%20exploitation%20unbridled%2C%20has%20seen%20the%20most%20dip%20in%20groundwater%20levels%20this%20summer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20why%20are%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20struggling%20so%20much%20with%20water%20scarcity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20perfect%20storm.%20What%20happened%20was%20that%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20get%20water%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20Phase-5%20project%20(delivering%20775%20million%20litres%20a%20day)%2C%20and%20that%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago.%20If%20this%20project%20had%20been%20completed%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20no%20crisis.%20With%20the%20completion%20of%20this%20project%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20Bengaluru%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20piped%20connection%20would%20have%20one%20with%20water%20flowing%20in%20it.%20But%20that%20project%20got%20delayed%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20May-June%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20some%20of%20the%20major%20city%20lakes%20have%20been%20drained%20and%20de-silted.%20That%20project%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20three%20years%20back%2C%20but%20this%20project%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20If%20you%20desilt%20and%20drain%20lakes%20for%20these%20many%20years%2C%20their%20capacity%20to%20recharge%20aquifers%20is%20non-existent.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20all%20the%20borewells%20have%20dried%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20however%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20is%20high%2C%20according%20to%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20the%20open%20recharge%20wells%20have%20sufficient%20water.%20Some%20of%20the%20lakes%2C%20which%20are%20full%20of%20water%2C%20are%20good%20for%20percolation.%20In%20these%20areas%2C%20the%20borewells%20are%20at%20a%20depth%20of%20150%20to%20300%20feet.%20Where%20there%20is%20no%20piped%20water%20supply%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20is%20very%20low.%20If%20the%20Cauvery%20Phase-5%20project%20is%20completed%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20water%20scarcity%20in%20the%20city%20will%20go%20away%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20If%20the%20lakes%20are%20filled%20with%20rainwater%20or%20tertiary%20treated%20wastewater%2C%20then%20the%20aquifers%20will%20be%20recharged%20and%20the%20problem%20will%20become%20a%20lot%20less%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vishwanath%20noted%20earlier%2C%20there%20are%20real%20problems%20that%20need%20to%20be%20solved%20to%20address%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345780%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-rain-reach-programme-hariharan-chandrashekhar-helps-children-in-bbmp-schools-conserve-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20scarcity%20in%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20article%2C%20we%20will%20highlight%20these%20problems%20and%20how%20we%20can%20solve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20c