ernal%20reuse%2C%20which%20means%20it%20is%20taken%20to%20Kolar%2C%20Chikkaballapur%2C%20and%20Devenahalli%2C%20where%20it%20is%20used%20to%20replenish%20both%20groundwater%20and%20surface%20water%20sources%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20remaining%20water%20flows%20into%20lakes%20and%20runs%20off%20land%20to%20join%20rivers%20downstream.%20This%20means%20the%20huge%20quantum%20of%20wastewater%20generated%20in%20the%20city%20is%20an%20untapped%20resource.%20Once%20treated%20to%20the%20required%20quality%2C%20wastewater%20can%20significantly%20mitigate%20freshwater%20consumption%20and%20can%20be%20crucial%20in%20making%20the%20city%20water%20resilient%20during%20low%20rainfall%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20sentiment%20that%20Vikas%20Brahmavar%2C%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoson%20Whitewater%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20water%20utility%20startup%2C%20shares.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20not%20have%20a%20city%20running%20on%20the%20hope%20of%20good%20rains.%20After%20all%2C%20if%20there%20are%20no%20rains%20till%20June%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20stress%20even%20on%20the%20municipal%20supply.%20We%20should%20have%20a%20city%20running%20on%20the%20hope%20of%20the%20wastewater%20flowing%20out%20and%20employ%20freshwater%20supply%20as%20a%20buffer%20for%20our%20everyday%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scarcity%20problem%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FVikas-Brahmavar-Boson-Whitewater-1712316714-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346666%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20Brahmavar%2C%20founder%20of%20Boson%20Whitewater%2C%20spoke%20to%20The%20Better%20India%20about%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20scarcity%20problem%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20any%20city%20in%20India%2C%20when%20authorities%20plan%20water%20distribution%2C%20they%20never%20look%20at%20what%20is%20going%20out%20of%20the%20city.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20developed%20cities%20like%20Singapore%2C%20the%20planning%20is%20not%20based%20on%20freshwater%20available%20in%20dams%20but%20based%20on%20the%20predictable%20wastewater%20which%20is%20going%20out%20of%20the%20city%2C%20because%20that%20can%20be%20estimated%20clearly%20based%20on%20the%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20population%20of%20a%20given%20city%20is%20known%2C%20authorities%20in%20places%20like%20Singapore%20know%20exactly%20the%20amount%20of%20wastewater%20which%20is%20going%20out.%20From%20the%20volume%20wastewater%20estimated%2C%20authorities%20can%20then%20gauge%20which%20industries%20can%20be%20covered%20by%20that%20treated%20wastewater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20policy%2C%20their%20starting%20point%20is%20wastewater%2C%20which%20addresses%20sanitation%20as%20well%20as%20industrial%20water%20requirements%2C%20and%20then%20they%20look%20at%20the%20freshwater%20available%20from%20dams%20or%20other%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20big%20mindset%20change%20has%20to%20come.%20Any%20developing%20country%20should%20have%20this%20mindset%20of%20looking%20at%20wastewater%20first%20before%20looking%20at%20freshwater%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Vikas.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boson%20Whitewater%20system%20converts%20treated%20wastewater%20into%20%E2%80%9Chigh-quality%20potable%20water%E2%80%9D.%20The%20setup%20has%20advanced%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341081%2Fiit-guwahati-phd-satyam-develops-affordable-iot-enabled-water-quality-purity-monitoring-device%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIoT%20(Internet%20of%20Things)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20AI%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337031%2Fbest-ai-innovations-by-indians-artificial-intelligence-startup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20machine%20learning%20(ML)%20enabled%2011-step%20filtration%20system%20to%20reduce%20physical%2C%20chemical%20and%20biological%20contaminants%20present%20in%20STP-treated%20wastewater.%20Currently%2C%20they%20work%20with%20industries%2C%20IT%20parks%2C%20malls%2C%20and%20apartment%20communities%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20recycle%20their%20wastewater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20their%2011-step%20filtration%20process%2C%20he%20claims%20that%20the%20water%20does%20not%20have%20any%20contaminants.%20%E2%80%9CE%20coli%2C%20coliforms%2C%20heavy%20metals%2C%20high%20hardness%2C%20pesticides%2C%20and%20herbicides%20are%20all%20removed%2C%20and%20the%20water%20is%20crystal%20clear%20and%20potable.%20National%20Accreditation%20Board%20for%20Testing%20and%20Calibration%20Laboratories%20(NABL)%20certified%20lab%20reports%20indicate%20the%20water%20is%20drinkable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solution%20to%20Bengaluru's%20Water%20Crisis%3F%20Boson%20Whitewater's%2011-step%20filtration%20system%20can%20convert%20treated%20wastewater%20into%20potable%20water%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610-300x174.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610-500x291.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610-768x447.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2FBoson-Whitewater-systeml-1667569610-150x87.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-302035%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolution%20to%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Water%20Crisis%3F%20Boson%20Whitewater%E2%80%99s%2011-step%20filtration%20system%20can%20convert%20treated%20wastewater%20into%20potable%20water%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20Boson%20is%20focused%20on%20this%20enormous%20volume%20of%20water%20which%20is%20going%20out%20of%20homes%2C%20apartments%2C%20and%20offices%20as%20treated%20wastewater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%