0they%20came%20up%20with%20the%20first%20recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20Johuree%20Lall%20Das%20had%20fled%20to%20the%20city%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Dubrajhat%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20Britishers%20were%20forcing%20Indians%20to%20engage%20in%20indigo%20cultivation.%20In%20Kolkata%2C%20he%20began%20making%20%3Cem%3Esandesh%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20a%20barrister%20Biswajit%20Ghosh%20of%20Pathuriaghata%20once%20gave%20Das%20cocoa%20powder%20that%20he%20brought%20back%20with%20him%20from%20his%20trip%20to%20England%20and%20challenged%20him%20to%20prepare%20the%20%3Cem%3Esandesh%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20the%20powder.%20Thus%2C%20Das%20made%20their%20very%20first%20chocolate%20%3Cem%3Esandesh%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20they%20continue%20to%20serve%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20KC%20Das%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20615px)%20100vw%2C%20615px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-175632-1710246423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KC%20Das%20invented%20the%20rosogolla%20in%201868%20and%20the%20mithai%20continues%20to%20be%20loved%20across%20India%20and%20the%20world%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-175632-1710246423.jpg%20615w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-175632-1710246423-283x300.jpg%20283w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-175632-1710246423-500x530.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-12-175632-1710246423-150x159.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344629%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKC%20Das%20invented%