ic-3-1712121488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-3-1712121488-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHeirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20he%20inherited%2018%20acres%20of%20land%20from%20his%20father.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20read%20Rachel%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20book%20%E2%80%98Silent%20Spring%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20highlighted%20the%20environmental%20harm%20caused%20by%20the%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20pesticides.%20Motivated%20by%20Carson%E2%80%99s%20message%2C%20Neelam%20resolved%20to%20transition%20his%20land%20into%20an%20organic%20farm.%20By%202003%2C%20he%20had%20successfully%20converted%20his%20entire%20acreage%20to%20organic%20cultivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20switching%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20I%20found%20out%20there%20were%20no%20organic%20seed%20varieties%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20some%20were%20accessible%20for%20rice%2C%20none%20were%20available%20for%20vegetables.%20The%20absence%20of%20reserves%20or%20authenticity%20in%20seed%20sources%20was%20concerning.%20Instead%2C%20the%20market%20was%20saturated%20with%20genetically%20modified%20hybrid%20seeds.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20worrying%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20also%20observed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20Northeast%20were%20switching%20to%20hybrid%20seeds%20and%20overlooked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315599%2Fhyderabad-chandana-naveen-gade-seedbasket-agro-services-sell-native-seeds-to-urban-gardeners%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheirloom%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Green%20Revolution%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20only%20hybrid%20seeds%20were%20to%20be%20supplied%20to%20the%20market%20to%20the%20farmers.%20This%20was%20never%20a%20solution%20for%20an%20%E2%80%98evergreen%E2%80%99%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20hybrid%20seeds%20offer%20higher%20yields%20in%20one%20season%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20saved%20for%20the%20following%20year.%20Consequently%2C%20farmers%20neglected%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20their%20sovereignty%20over%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%20Since%20then%2C%20Neelam%E2%80%99s%20mission%20has%20been%20to%20conserve%20decade-old%20seeds%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20the%20traditional%20wisdom%20imparted%20by%20his%20father%20and%20the%20elderly%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20set%20out%20in%20search%20of%20these%20heirloom%20treasures.%20In%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Neelam%20has%20conserved%20nearly%20800%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%20like%20tomatoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20capsicum%2C%20basil%2C%20and%20200%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331636%2Fassam-farmer-starts-rice-library-grows-preserves-indigenous-rice-varieties%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20rice%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Cem%3Emadhuri%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Enanyya%20rice%2C%20sticky%20gum%20rice%2C%20black%20rice%2C%20soft%20rice%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ejoha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20seeds%20have%20their%20own%20identity%20in%20terms%20of%20taste%2C%20colour%2C%20and%20shape.%20They%20are%20adaptable%20to%20the%20diverse%20Indian%20climatic%20zones.%20In%20one%20way%2C%20they%20are%20more%20resilient%20than%20hybrid%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHybrid%20vs%20heirloom%20seeds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-farming-1-1712236952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346541%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20difference%20between%20hybrid%20and%20heirloom%20seeds%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20hybrid%20varieties%20give%20more%20yield%2C%20they%20are%20produced%20via%20genetic%20manipulation.%20We%20compel%20hybrid%20seeds%20to%20grow%20using%20external%20fertilisers%20and%20chemicals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Haryana%20are%20extremely%20dependent%20on%20these%20outside%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20further%20points%20out%20that%2C%20unlike%20heirloom%20varieties%2C%20the%20seed%20saved%20from%20hybrids%20does%20not%20grow%20true%20to%20its%20type%20in%20the%20next%20cycle.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20be%20less%20vigorous%20and%20more%20genetically%20variable.%20If%20you%20cannot%20replicate%20it%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20keeping%20the%20seeds.%20It%20only%20compels%20farmers%20to%20buy%20new%20seeds%20every%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20heirloom%20seeds%20are%20genetically%20diverse%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20chemical-laden%20fertilisers%2C%20and%20are%20naturally%20resistant%20to%20disease%20and%20pests.%20As%20they%20are%20open-pollinated%2C%20you%20can%20easily%20replicate%20those%20seeds%20next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20produce%20harvested%20from%20both%20varieties%20differ%2C%20Neelam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20tomatoes%20are%20available%20year-round%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20past%20when%20we%20only%20had%20them%20in%20winter.%20To%20satisfy%20demand%2C%20farmers%20now%20grow%20tomatoes%20in%20mountainous%20areas%20with%20heavy%20fertiliser%20use.%20However%2C%20organically%20grown%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20respective%20seasons%20may%20not%20last%20as%20long%20but%20are%20richer%20in%20nutrients%2C%20tastier%2C%20and%20more%20vibrant%20in%20colour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20France%2C%20various%20tomato%20varieties%20were%20once%20used%20in%20different%20recipes%2C%20but%20now%20a%20single%2C%20sweeter%20tomato%20is%20used%20universally%2C%20replacing%20the%20sour%20ones%20of%20the%20past.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Forganic-2-1-1712121421-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346321%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeelam%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20says%20he%20wanted%20the%20local%20farmers%20in%20his%20region%20to%20wholeheartedly%20adopt%20and%20switch%20to%20heirloom%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20point%20doing%20all%20this%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20work%20received%20a%20great%20response%20from%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20going%20beyond%20conserving%20seeds%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Neelam%20now%20trains%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20in%20seed%20conservation.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2024%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20Northeast%20%E2%80%94%20including%20states%20like%20Nagaland%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20them%20grow%20and%20conserve%20their%20own%20heirloom%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20year%2C%20Neelam%20sells%20approximately%208%2C000%20packets%20of%20heirloom%20seeds%20at%20Rs%2099%20each%20to%20farmers.%20With%20these%20seeds%20and%20the%20training%20he%20provides%2C%20farmers%20can%20cultivate%20crops%20and%20harvest%20new%20seeds%20for%20the%20next%20cycle%2C%20ensuring%20sustainable%20food%20security%20%E2%80%94%20a%20goal%20Neelam%20passionately%20pursues%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20Diganata%20Bora%20has%20been%20cultivating%20vegetables%20using%20such%20heirloom%20seeds%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm%20in%20Paschim%20Manjiri%20village%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompared%20to%20hybrid%20varieties%2C%20we%20get%20good%20yield%20using%20heirloom%20ones.%20In%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5B0.33%20acre%5D%2C%20we%20now%20get%206-7%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20over%202-2.5%20quintals.%20Additionally%2C%20our%20input%20expenses%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%20as%20we%20use%20readily%20available%20cow%20dung%20as%20fertiliser.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20have%20decided%20to%20switch%3B%20now%20our%20soil%20fertility%20has%20also%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Diganata%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeelam%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBack%20when%20I%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176277%2Fkarnataka-bengaluru-organic-farming-native-seeds-woman%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20were%20no%20resources%20available%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20from.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20happy%20to%20have%20created%20a%20helpful%20platform%20for%20other%20farmers.%20When%20I%20visit%20their%20fields%2C%20I%20feel%20great%20to%20see%20the%20joy%20on%20their%20faces.%20By%20cultivating%20their%20own%20organic%20seeds%20and%20crops%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20agriculture%20economically%20viable%20in%20our%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Neelam%20Dutta.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712239080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alarmed%20by%20the%20effect%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20food%20security%2C%20Assam-based%20Neelam%20Dutta%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20safeguard%20heirloom%20seeds.%20Under%20his%20venture%20%E2%80%98Pabhoi%20Greens%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%2024%2C000%20farmers%20in%20Northeast%20India%20in%20organic%20cultivation%20and%20seed%20preservation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346317%2Fassam-organic-farmer-neelam-dutta-conserves-climate-resilient-heirloom-seeds-pabhoi-greens-northeast%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Selling%20Lemonade%20To%20Building%20a%20108-YO%20Dairy%20Empire%3A%20Journey%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Loved%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20if%20anyone%20were%20to%20ask%20veteran%20Bollywood%20actress%20Mumtaz%20where%20she%20was%20heading%20on%20a%20hot%20summer%20afternoon%2C%20she%E2%80%99d%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%2C%20of%20course%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20the%20years%2C%20her%20answer%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20changed.%20Today%2C%20Mumtaz%20is%20not%20the%20only%20name%20on%20the%20influential%20guest%20list.%20Also%20featured%20are%20actors%20Jim%20Sarbh%20and%20Boman%20Irani.%20For%20a%20business%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295229%2Ftaj-icecream-mumbai-eatery-loved-by-madhubala-makes-natural-icecream-in-wooden-barrels%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20draw%20for%20celebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Ambanis%2C%20the%20Birlas%2C%20and%20the%20Tatas%2C%20they%20must%20be%20doing%20something%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20anyone%20will%20affirm%2C%20a%20menu%20boasting%20scrumptious%20sweets%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20draw%20of%20this%20dairy%20venture%20located%20off%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Princess%20Street.%20It%20is%20its%20century-old%20charm%20and%20the%20recipe%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20where%20the%20magic%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20wondering%20why%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20continued%20to%20see%20an%20unwavering%20customer%20base%20for%20over%20108%20years%20now%2C%20the%20proof%20is%20literally%20and%20metaphorically%20in%20the%20pudding.%20The%20history%20of%20the%20business%20ties%20back%20to%20when%20a%20young%20boy%20of%2016%20began%20delivering%20milk%20cans%20to%20homes%20around%20Kalbadevi%20(an%20old%20neighbourhood%20in%20Mumbai).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20Nariman%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20of%20a%20job.%20Circumstances%20led%20him%20to%20it%2C%20and%20ambition%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20success.%20Since%201916%2C%20when%20Ardeshir%20sold%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327249%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-on-electricy-bills-gau-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20can%20of%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20seen%20its%20trajectory%20of%20ups%20interspersed%20with%20downs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20fourth%20generation%20settles%20down%20to%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%2