%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20old%20machinery%20such%20as%20the%20Gerber%2C%20the%20weighing%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20pasteuriser%20have%20still%20been%20preserved%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-5-1711120589-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20old%20machinery%20such%20as%20the%20Gerber%2C%20the%20weighing%20scale%2C%20and%20the%20pasteuriser%20have%20still%20been%20preserved%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Zeenia%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sarfaraz%20points%20out%20that%20this%20consistency%20is%20what%20has%20kept%20them%20relevant%20even%20today%2C%20the%20cousins%20emphasise%20that%20the%20staff%20who%20work%20with%20them%20are%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20the%20family.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CRight%20from%20the%20senior%20heads%20of%20the%20company%20to%20the%20person%20who%20sweeps%20the%20floor%2C%20everybody%20puts%20in%20absolute%20effort.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20makes%20us%20what%20we%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20has%20been%20winning%20the%20hearts%20and%20palates%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s