oduced%20the%20micro-irrigation%20scheme%20in%202005-06%2C%20under%20which%20subsidies%20were%20provided%20for%20drip%20and%20sprinkler%20irrigation.%20Saravanan%2C%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20many%20such%20new%3Cbr%3Eschemes%2C%20decided%20to%20give%20drip%20irrigation%20a%20try.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20face%20water%20scarcity%2C%20which%20made%20irrigation%20very%20difficult.%20Drip%20irrigation%20saves%20water%20and%20irrigates%20thrice%20the%20amount%20of%20land%20using%20the%20same%20water%20used%20by%20traditional%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saravanan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202007%2C%20the%20farmer%20has%20moved%20to%20drip%20irrigation%20on%20his%206%20acre%20and%2036%20cents%20(1%20acre%20is%20100%20cents)%20land%20on%20which%20he%20cultivates%20turmeric%2C%20groundnuts%2C%20and%20vegetables.%20He%20also%20practises%20integrated%20farming%2C%20a%20sustainable%20agricultural%20system%20where%20crops%2C%20livestock%2C%20aquaculture%2C%20poultry%20are%20managed%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%20crops%2C%20he%20also%20manages%20livestock%2C%20including%20cows%2C%20goats%2C%20ducks%20and%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20he%20started%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20he%20got%20his%20soil%20tested.%20The%20test%20indicated%20that%20the%20soil%20was%20not%20healthy%2C%20and%20had%20rising%20pH%20levels%20and%20was%20getting%20spoilt.%20This%20was%20the%20same%20time%20when%20his%20turmeric%20crop%20was%20affected%20by%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20uses%20innovative%20methods%20of%20farming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan3-1712146605-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20uses%20innovative%20methods%20of%20farming%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20at%20the%20KVK%20suggested%20some%20biofertilisers%20to%20salvage%20the%20turmeric%20crop%2C%20and%20it%20worked.%20They%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20preserve%20the%20soil%20and%20prevent%20further%20damage%20was%20by%20moving%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%2058-year-old.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%202008%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20save%20his%20land%2C%20soil%20and%20crops%2C%20he%20slowly%20stopped%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides.%20He%20also%20started%20practising%20crop%20rotation%20to%20ensure%20soil%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20I%20plant%20pulses%2C%20I%20ensure%20that%20I%20change%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20year.%20I%20also%20planted%20nerium%20as%20a%20border%20crop%20to%20absorb%20pollutants%20and%20grow%20%3Cem%3Eagathi%20%3C%2Fem%3E%26amp%3B%20maize%20around%20the%20field%20as%20a%20barrier%20crop%20to%20prevent%20the%20entry%20of%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20constructed%20a%20vermicompost%20production%20unit%20in%202008%20which%20produces%20over%206%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20He%20uses%20this%20vermicompost%2C%20neem%20cakes%20and%20castor%20cakes%20as%20fertilisers.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20biogas%20plant%20that%20converts%20the%20waste%20into%20energy%20and%20purifies%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%2C%20he%20utilises%20%3Cem%3Epanchakavya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20solution%20made%20of%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20ghee%2C%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20used%20as%20a%20fertiliser)%20spray%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20homemade%20spray%20containing%20ginger%2C%20garlic%20%26amp%3B%20chillies%20for%20controlling%20pests%20and%20disease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20everything%20was%20going%20well%2C%20Saravanan%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20grow%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle.%20Buying%20it%20from%20outside%20was%20expensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20in%202011%2C%20KVK%20Namakkal%20conducted%20a%20demonstration%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20hydroponic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20maize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20maize%20in%20a%20cupboard%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20696px)%20100vw%2C%20696px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20grows%20maize%20fodder%20in%20his%20cupboard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072.jpeg%20696w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-245x300.jpeg%20245w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-500x613.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-02-at-7.26.52-PM-1712146072-150x184.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20grows%20maize%20fodder%20in%20his%20cupboard%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fodder%20demand%20was%20increasing%20and%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20keep%20up.%20The%20existing%20land%20was%20just%20not%20sufficient%20to%20grow%20fodder.%20While%20I%20saw%20the%20demo%20in%202011%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20few%20years%20later%20that%20I%20got%20access%20to%20the%20kit%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Saravanan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Aavin%20the%20dairy%20co-operative%20in%20Namakkal%2C%20gave%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%20to%20Saravanan.%20Hydroponics%20is%20a%20technique%20of%20growing%20plants%20without%20soil%20and%20very%20little%20water.%20It%20uses%20a%20water-based%20solution%20and%20produces%20fodder%2C%20cereals%20and%20pulses%20on%20a%20small%20scale%20level.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20explains%20that%20by%20planting%20500%20gm%20of%20maize%2C%20he%20gets%204.5-5%20kg%20of%20maize%20fodder%20in%20a%20matter%20of%208%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20keep%20the%20trays%20in%20my%20cupboard%20as%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20sunlight.%20Since%20it%20grows%20in%208%20days%2C%20I%20get%20a%20sufficient%20yield%20in%20a%20month.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20pushing%20other%20farmers%20too%20to%20try%20hydroponics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20costs%20about%20Rs%2020%2C000.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20explains%20the%20steps%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327478%2Fashwin-sawant-low-cost-hydroponics-model-helps-farmers-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaize%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20a%20hydroponics%20unit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWash%20and%20soak%20the%20grains%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETie%20the%20seeds%20in%20a%20gunny%20bag%20and%20keep%20it%20in%20water%20for%2024%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETransfer%20the%20sprouted%20seeds%20to%20a%20tray%20and%20spread%20it%20out.%20Keep%20it%20in%20the%20cupboard.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20it%20once%20every%20three%20hours%2C%20either%20manually%20or%20using%20a%20sprinkler%20with%20a%20timer%20for%207%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20yield%20will%20be%20ready%20on%20the%208th%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EPicture%20credits%3A%20P%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712147266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fsaravanan-min-1712145955.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22P%20Saravanan%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20uses%20hydroponics%20to%20grow%20maize%20fodder%20for%20his%20cattle.%20He%20has%20also%20found%20a%20way%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20pesticides%20and%20keep%20his%20produce%20healthy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346387%2Forganic-farmer-namakkal-tamil-nadu-hydroponics-maize-fodder-drip-irrigation-p-saravanan%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20is%20Empowering%202500%20Indian%20Women%20Scale%20Their%20Micro%20Enterprises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20India%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship%20taking%20centre%20stage.%20The%20Economic%20Survey%20of%202023%20highlights%20a%20surge%20in%20entrepreneurship%20which%20is%20not%20only%20setting%20a%20precedent%20for%20the%20future%20generations%20but%20changing%20the%20concept%20of%20employment.%20The%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20will%20create%20over%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%20(ISB)%2C%20through%20their%20one-of-a-kind%20%E2%80%98I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20programme%20is%20providing%20the%20required%20support%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20championing%20entrepreneurship%20for%20every%20section%20of%20the%20society%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20purview%2C%20there%20are%20various%20programmes%20all%20fostering%20entrepreneurship%20and%20nurturing%20startups%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20%E2%80%98Start-to-Scale%E2%80%99%20support%20that%20will%20accelerate%20their%20conversion%20into%20profitable%20ventures.%20One%20such%20recently%20launched%20programme%20%E2%80%98DiscoverShe%E2%80%99%2C%20brings%20together%20the%20goals%20of%20a%20profitable%20venture%20while%20upholding%20the%20inclusion%20of%20women%20in%20business%20by%20empowering%20women%20micro-entrepreneurs%20to%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20series%20of%20%3Cem%3Eyatras%3C%2Fem%3E%20(roadshows)%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20of%20India%2C%20DiscoverShe%20is%20set%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20these%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20pitch%20their%20ideas%20and%20engage%20with%20investors%2C%20mentors%20and%20other%20stakeholders.%20But%20as%20Saumya%20Kumar%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20highlights%2C%20a%20significant%20obstacle%20hindering%20the%20growth%20of%20women-led%20businesses%20in%20India%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20micro-financing%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334411%2Ftop-women-entrepreneurs-in-food-industry-india-inspiring-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20encounter%20challenges%20due%20to%20low%20CIBIL%20scores%20(%3Cem%3Ea%20numerical%20figure%20that%20denotes%20one%E2%80%99s%20creditworthiness%20and%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20how%20well%20they%20have%20managed%20their%20finances%3C%2Fem%3E)%20which%20impacts%20their%20creditworthiness%20and%20raises%20speculations%20about%20their%20ability%20to%20manage%20the%20finances%20of%20their%20own%20business.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20women%20entrepreneurs%20with%20brilliant%20ideas%20and%20business%20acumen%20find%20it%20particularly%20difficult%20to%20procure%20financing%20for%20their%20business%20ventures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20has%20launched%20a%20novel%20programme%20'DiscoverShe'%20that%20empowers%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20scale%20their%20businesses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstartups-1712050414-150x79.jpg%20150w%